{
 "name": "RPlog_Enter_Darth_Malign",
 "title": "Enter Darth Malign",
 "summary": "Aboard the smuggler Axel Vichten's flamboyant ship Purple Haze, hidden in a quiet orbit, Axel hosts CDU Rear Admiral Naten Bonrue and his NIO escort in a surveillance-proof armory to discuss the Imperial deserters Dareus and Lynae Caiton, sought by Rear Admiral Petra Doom. Axel proposes handing the traitors, dead, to the Empire to keep an Inquisition team off Caspar, while revealing it was he who exposed the warlord Danik Kreldin's plot against the Emperor and that he intends to profit from the chaos. Bonrue, unwilling to risk the CDU but valuing Axel's intelligence, counsels patience and the option of faked substitute bodies, just as the Sith Inquisitor Darth Malign, also known to Axel by his old name Tyler Damion, radios for landing clearance and enters in a wave of dark energy. Malign, now Director of Imperial Diplomatic Operations, lets Bonrue depart, then uses postcognition to read the room and presses Axel for the truth. He grants Axel permission to stall Petra Doom with fabricated Nar Shaddaa leads in exchange for tracking down the real traitors, but when Axel rashly threatens what the Empire would face at Caspar, Malign erupts in furious menace, warning him not to fail, before stalking out and leaving the shaken smuggler alive.",
